{"tid":2463144,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳雲老師：運河擱淺係做戲","createTime":"2021-03-26T13:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T13:14:44.000Z","uid":78768,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4419e10912177e6228c5638aa8091d9b4a04bffa","tid":2463144,"uid":78768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"//陳雲：這樣子叫擱淺？騙誰啊。只要開動引擎就能解決。人類好騙，這副擱淺樣子，就像用弱感冒來封鎖全世界一年以上那樣！<br />\n這場爛戲是侮辱人類吧，起碼要撞爆河堤，將貨櫃倒滿河底，這樣才像樣！//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmThGdASqxebvi1ihHGe9X5NvcTP6ofmjY2Ys1gfTmuVBk?filename=aKKnORT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKKnORT.png&h=c29f9ab0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0221ca8f481003b385c26c7971777f4ca014793c","tid":2463144,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:09:29.000Z","msg":"所謂熱狗式放負，即係無論你做乜佢地都會揾到嘢鬧，最好乜都唔好做，因為唔做就自然唔會出錯，正正因為咩都唔做，正合極權所需，而如果真係咩都唔做，佢哋又會笑你咩都唔做輸啦輸啦，雞蛋挑骨頭就係熱狗式放負嘅一大特色"},{"pid":"d2f1eed548ae4a9de25db45aa3fad66b079fcc08","tid":2463144,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73c4a7fd0a530448c9585548cd880c2e5b59fea","tid":2463144,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:10:49.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫擱淺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2472bdf059719e331fd30c20b1d3843b4b518ce1","tid":2463144,"uid":154373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:11:54.000Z","msg":"樓上又有件精神分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aee19d422fd6a7a5bca9c8a39646283e00a62a1","tid":2463144,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f73c4a7fd0a530448c9585548cd880c2e5b59fea","tid":2463144,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T13:10:49.000Z","msg":"知唔知咩叫擱淺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor